Third-Party Model Licenses
==========================

This project includes imported system dynamics models from third-party
sources. These models (both the original Vensim .mdl files and their
derived JSON and Java representations) are distributed under their
original licenses, separate from the project source code license (AGPL-3.0).

All third-party model content resides under:
  - forrester-app/src/main/resources/models/   (JSON definitions)
  - forrester-demos/src/main/java/             (generated Java demo classes)
  - models/Vensim/                             (original .mdl files from Vensim)

Generated Java demo classes derived from third-party models carry a
file-level license header indicating CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0.

